{"tid":1648573,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"行動post2.0：核彈NBA文宣，聚首修頓","createTime":"2019-10-12T09:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T05:00:44.000Z","uid":332024,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"958ec0f16ae52284dc382d34609df3f10f05c379","tid":1648573,"uid":332024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"之前嗰個出得柒咗，而家再黎過！<br />\n<br />\n得近排NBA發生咩事唔使我講，我真係屌哂你哋老母啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國球迷眾籌派T-Shirt，全美國人屌到支共七彩，你哋除咗笑鳩大陸冇得睇NBA做咗啲咩啊？NBA分分鐘跪，老味你哋唔幫手，陣間跪咗係咪我哋罷睇啊？<br />\n<br />\n所以，繼英超大和解後，到香港NBA球迷聚首修頓！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期：10月14日<br />\n<br />\n時間：20：00-23：00<br />\n<br />\n地點：修頓球場<br />\n<br />\nDress code：不拘，建議NBA波衫或打波裝束<br />\n<br />\n記住，本次行動為純和理非，製作核彈文宣，見到記者記得要多謝美國球迷<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔推唔到post，文宣同波友幫手啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdae77bbc47291c1ad6b7c5fe1141c9cf774e6a","tid":1648573,"uid":332024,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fL9CaZq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfL9CaZq.jpg&h=791f1ec4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"565986ddf10c9650ac0e88435f1510d42df08332","tid":1648573,"uid":332024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ev3rOMj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEv3rOMj.png&h=33968dcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3e23c1dcf8694649e4a9382fb33