":"7647e71b0f738c3f5ec040081256f8e61523f667","tid":1648573,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"10月14人權法集會呀<br />\n一日一event"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"轉日期唔係問題，但照幫手推咗先，等大家知道有呢個event"},{"pid":"739e1998cf75919467db841d3e6a2ecb77919fce","tid":1648573,"uid":321119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全世界跟隊打波！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"57bd6ac1933e98e483718f0c47ad439674c4a81b","tid":1648573,"uid":227819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:35:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"25a60738b9663d894f48d91f65d0fd4e735a9892","tid":1648573,"uid":332024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"經過小弟深思熟慮，為免分散，決定改期至10月15號（星期二）<br />\n<br />\n係時候黎個有氣勢嘅宣言：<br />\n<br />\n籃球教我們勇於仗義執言<br />\n<br />\n香港反修例運動延續至今已有四個多月，事件所引申出的警隊濫捕濫暴、香港民主進程、人道狀況、高度自治⋯⋯等等問題令社會各界紛紛為是次各種不公義而發聲，而事件亦已經發酵至國際層面。<br />\nNBA休斯頓火箭隊總經理Daryl Morey早前亦曾於其個人twitter發表&ldquo;Fight for freedom, stand with Hong Kong &rdquo;，之後受到中國各方口誅筆伐，並要脅NBA制裁Morey。雖然NBA拒絕應中國各方所求，而中國的抵制行動未見成效。但作為本地籃球迷，看見有海外籃球界人士為我們的家園所發聲，我們又怎能視而不見，又怎能不團結我們的力量去出一分力呢？<br />\n香港嘅籃球人，打波要出聲提隊友，睇波要出聲為愛隊打氣，見到球證吹錯都會出聲鬧啦，而家大是大非面前你唔係唔出嚟，你唔係唔出聲，你唔係唔表態呀？<br />\n嗱，我哋唔係想起大台，有idea歡迎提出一齊改改佢，最重要係我哋呢班鍾意籃球嘅人，可以喺呢晚聚埋一齊表態，同埋互相鼓勵吓大家！香港人，反抗！<br />\n香港之路Basketball Version！<br />\n召喚所有有良知嘅籃球愛好者，星期一，夜晚八點，修頓街場見！<br />\n<br />\n香港之路 Basketball Version!<br />\n日期:10月15日(星期二)<br />\n地點:修頓室外場 （無場紙 可能要打個場番黎又或者如果你卜左同我講聲 唔該）<br />\n時間:晚上7時30分<br />\nDress code:<br />\nNBA球衣(其他籃球裝束亦可，黑色為佳)，有波帶波！流感高峰期，請帶口罩，預防感染！<br />\n流程:<br />\n20:00 人鍊組成Morey字樣 Stand with Morey!<br />\n20:15 集氣嗌口號<br />\n20:30 頌唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n籃球教會我們勇於仗義執言<br />\n#光復香港時代革命<br />\n#fightforfreedomstandwithhk<br />\n#standwithmorey"},{"pid":"3686d40f965d3d88c9330fb3ab3a15b6563465a4","tid":1648573,"uid":332024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:15:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/IMokUUn5tyHzlw72kAD1Tg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FIMokUUn5tyHzlw72kAD1Tg&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=76922c85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/IMokUUn5tyHzlw72kAD1Tg</a><br />\n<br />\n聚首修頓TG group"},{"pid":"0fcedd45bfdad85c15a7fc4e4a0bdc15a0a6a21f","tid":1648573,"uid":300424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP牌仔無力一推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1203a57dccb85b9801768f396ea6ff9c6e2745","tid":1648573,"uid":300424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"樓主， 點解唔係NBA開幕日 搞既？"},{"pid":"b3af03f21660cd00a0a68b1b5a5edfe2e8100509","tid":1648573,"uid":222865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d9bd43b5cff3ee3839187709325517f5c27a67","tid":1648573,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b995e017ac3dc5fad14a36d9656e743c14aa0d","tid":1648573,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99fec2274c9d9cd4b2f4e586caf50d56fffce03","tid":1648573,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4509dfc83322d083c8647179bee8df4bcb748701","tid":1648573,"uid":229886,"like":0,"disli